data.title: Intel and Oracle Cloud Partnership
data.meta_description: Oracle and Intel have worked closely for more than 25 years bringing enterprise class solutions that are innovative, reliable, scalable and secure.
data.text:
Oracle Cloud Services and Intel - A Platform for Innovation

Oracle Cloud services built on IntelÂ® technology offers best-in-class services across software as a service (SaaS), platform as a service (PaaS), and infrastructure as a service (IaaS). You can even put Oracle Cloud in your own data center.
